   ALL NEWS STORIES

   [logo2.png]

   Since 2005, Preventeo has been designing, developing and marketing an
   innovative SaaS platform for management systems administration.

   Over the past 10 years, Preventeo has become a benchmark platform for
   compliance, risk and operational management in France, combining
   cloud-based software/business solutions with expert consulting.

   More than 200 clients, including large multinationals, use the
   Preventeo platform every day.

   A collaborative, secure workstation that functions as a single point of
   entry, the Preventeo platform allows its users, centrally and at
   subsidiary level, to manage business processes and access all their
   applications, associated documentation and applicable legal
   requirements.
